humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The report states 'Lymph nodes: 0/10 positive for metastasis (Axillary 0/10)'. This means that out of the 10 assessed lymph nodes, none of them had metastases. Based on New Rule 11, N0 can indicate that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage for this patient's cancer is N0.
